{"tid":1507070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[外國/Twitter文宣] Hong Kong Protest Travel 正式上線","createTime":"2019-08-26T04:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T09:37:15.000Z","uid":14699,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"263de1cbc3beb86d88217d14781f0cfc6c685f92","tid":1507070,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:18:43.000Z","msg":"之前有個po講好多外國人都表示好想支持香港人但唔知有點先可以幫到手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1472787/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1472787/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港作為好客之都<br />\n不妨對外國人宣傳<br />\ntake個short trip黎香港感受一下前線氣氛<br />\n政府又成日話我地班廢青影響經濟<br />\n而家就推廣全球獨一既另類旅遊體驗<br />\n<br />\n如果遊行當中歐美多國有0.00001%&nbsp;既supporters 黎香港拎住自已支national flag行係好明顯 <br />\n可以向國際社會帶出強而有力既fight for freedom msg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019 香港成為左爭取民主自由既最前線 <br />\nconnect國際社會 攜手對抗極權政府<br />\n抗爭者當中不乏高學歴人士 <br />\n英文解說相信難唔到大家<br />\nSIR, THIS WAY<br />\n<br />\n要比旅客最新資訊<br />\n長期有update既link係好重要<br />\n靠旅發局真係死得<br />\n小妹記憶力有限 歡迎補充<br />\n整合完亦可以印qr code係機場派傳單<br />\n<br />\nProtest Schedule<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/HKersCampaignSchedule\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FHKersCampaignSchedule&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=3ff3c2a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/HKersCampaignSchedule</a><br />\n<br />\n香港民主運動 2019 時序歷程 <br />\nHong Kong Movement 2019 Timeline<br />\n<a href=\"https://tl.hkrev.info/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftl.hkrev.info%2Fen%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=b49f7505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tl.hkrev.info/en/</a><br />\n<br />\nReal time protest location map<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=888b6f6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<br />\n連儂牆位置<br />\nLennon Wall in Hong Kong<br />\n(唔知有冇巴打mark 過location 落 google map 可以share返)<br />\n<a href=\"http://timable.com/zh-hk/event/1825867\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fevent%2F1825867&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=6f49c9e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://timable.com/zh-hk/event/1825867</a><br />\n<br />\n香港良心米之連地圖 <br />\nHong Kong Conscience Shop Map<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/43jwMgvJm4eq4qE16\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2F43jwMgvJm4eq4qE16&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTY2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=526297c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/43jwMgvJm4eq4qE16</a><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論 <br />\n歡迎整合更多不同資訊同出文宣圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GjQ7aua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGjQ7aua.jpg&h=7bb9549c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#FightForFreedom <br />\n#StandWithHK<br />\n#HongKongProtests<br />\n#Eye4HK<br />\n#EyeforHK<br />\n#NopoliceBrutality<br />\n#FreeFromFear<br />\n#DemocracyForHK<br />\n#ChiNazi <br />\n#ZiNa <br />\n#NaChi<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"bcdb18bdc8de31455c3fbaff58d6dc63408ed221","tid":1507070,"uid":65888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"［國際文宣］91機場要預先對外國文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507063</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c81855657a9d587c0d634bb7277c304774032ad","tid":1507070,"uid":14699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"928a6772ecc4848ddaaf2ff1e241422dbefbcbd0","tid":1507070,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki